00:16:21.510 --> 00:16:25.180
Anlıyorum...  
Peki bu kimin nesi?!  

00:16:27.930 --> 00:16:28.760
Oh!  

00:16:41.060 --> 00:16:43.510
O... daha önceki!  

00:16:46.810 --> 00:16:47.930
Kagero Hanım...  

00:16:49.930 --> 00:16:51.510
O bir Fuuma Jounin.  

00:16:52.100 --> 00:16:53.220
Sasame!  

00:16:55.970 --> 00:16:57.060
Sasame...  

00:16:58.140 --> 00:17:03.140
Lord Orochimaru tarafından  
diriltildim...  

00:17:03.680 --> 00:17:06.720
Sen! Orochimaru seni  
kandırıyor!  

00:17:06.810 --> 00:17:08.260
Sasuke nerede?  

00:17:08.350 --> 00:17:12.510
